articles.title: Asia markets mostly rise after Wall Street's mixed moves that saw investors rotate out of tech stocks - CNBC
articles.description: Asia-Pacific markets trade higher even after a mixed session on Wall Street.
articles.content:
Asia-Pacific markets mostly rose Tuesday after a mixed session on Wall Street that saw the Dow soar and the Nasdaq slip as investors rotated out of tech stocks.
